				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "PAD where a character who doesn't have the ointment applied steps into the shadowcurse and considers applying some. \r\nOnly triggers if someone has spare ointment in their inventory. (At least one application)\r\nPlays only if 2 or more characters present: first to speak doesn't have the ointment applied on them. SH speaks first if she can.\r\nWRITER, don't forget to update the voicebark file SCL_ShadowCurse_VB_WantsOintment if you change the structure here!"
				}
